flowchart LR
  user[User priorities and field history]
  planner[Observation planner]
  queue[Onboard sensor task queue]
  sensor[Candidate land tile acquisition]
  features[Onboard feature extractor]
  policy[Triage policy]
  packets[Bounded packet queue]
  downlink[Downlink manager]
  ground[Ground calibrator]
  delivery[User worklist or alert]
  ecostress[ECOSTRESS calibration context]

  user --> planner
  planner --> queue
  queue --> sensor
  sensor --> features
  features --> policy
  policy -->|priority_chip| packets
  policy -->|feature_summary| packets
  policy -->|defer| queue
  packets --> downlink
  downlink --> ground
  ecostress --> ground
  ground --> delivery
  ground --> planner
